This is replay part for malloc-tracing facility (see
https://github.com/alk/gperftools/tree/wip-malloc-tracing)

After getting trace like this:

$ LD_PRELOAD=$PREFIX/lib/libtcmalloc_minimal_tracing.so TCMALLOC_TRACE_OUTPOUT=file.lz4 ./your-program

Recommended usage is like this:

$ ./postprocess raw-trace-file | ./bump-pipes.rb lz4 >processed-trace.lz4

$ dd if=processed-trace.lz4 bs=1M iflag=direct | ./bump-pipes.rb lz4 -d | ./replay
